PrecisOrder accepting a document intitled "AMENDMENT TO A DESIGNATION" duly approved by the TSUU T'INA NATION Band of Indians whereby the band will permit the Department of National Defence to use a part of Sarcee Indian Reserve No. 145 until June 5, 2010, in accordance with the Sarcee Training Area Settlement Agreement.

precis:
Order accepting a document intitled "AMENDMENT TO A DESIGNATION" duly
approved by the TSUU T'INA NATION Band of Indians whereby the band will
permit the Department of National Defence to use a part of Sarcee Indian
Reserve No. 145 until June 5, 2010, in accordance with the Sarcee Training
Area Settlement Agreement.
